# 📝 TL;DR

- Try to survive while doing as much damage as you can to farm as much Cash as you can.

---

# 🎮 Playstyle

- Use Javelin Spin to deflect any easy damage to protect yourself and do damage at the same time.

---

# ⚡ Power

- [Spynstem Update](item_9fbbe756-5dd6-44f6-abd8-a8355f0be2b5) is core to the build as we will use to generate a lot of Ultimate Charge.

---

# 🧰 Items

- [Power Playbook](item_6d8803cf-baa7-46ee-af91-51e7f2301418): Increases the damage returned from [Spynstem Update](item_9fbbe756-5dd6-44f6-abd8-a8355f0be2b5) and more damage from Javelin Spin.
- [Winning Attitude](item_8714087c-c078-4619-a2ef-327bc6edaa69): If you're like me and you suck at Orisa, you're probably going to die a bit and this will reward our feeding with some extra Ultimate Charge.
- [Charged Plating](item_b8ca58e7-6ae2-40ee-8618-fe2f32315295): This will effectively provide 2 items of value in 1 by using our extra Ultimate Charge from [Spynstem Update](item_9fbbe756-5dd6-44f6-abd8-a8355f0be2b5) and [Winning Attitude](item_8714087c-c078-4619-a2ef-327bc6edaa69) to benefit from it sooner.

---

notes:
# 📝 TL;DR

- Farm Cash and learn how to survive against what the enemy has and what you can use to farm Ultimate Charge using Javelin Spin's deflect.

---

# 🎮 Playstyle

- Keeping trying to do as much damage as you can to farm up Cash as best you can. Use these rounds to understand how your cooldowns are best used to survive against the enemy team while using Javelin Spin to deflect damage for Ultimate Charge.

---

# 🧰 Items

-  [Elite Rotator Cuff](item_dfba3349-64b8-4386-8eaf-15bcd1ca6b37): Longer Javelin Spins = More Deflect for Ultimate Charge
-  [Multi-Tool](item_5ba8d94e-f2f3-44b7-8773-025fc6ed7c56) is some extra AP and CDR, both of which we can get some use of.

## 🔄 Optional Items

- Replace  [Multi-Tool](item_5ba8d94e-f2f3-44b7-8773-025fc6ed7c56) with  [Refraction Tiles](item_16e4b34e-d8dd-4cbd-85dc-ff6370cca092) if you're against beams like Zarya, or even Mei, if they're focusing you.

---

# 💸 Low Cash

- Sell Green Items if you need to.  [Elite Rotator Cuff](item_dfba3349-64b8-4386-8eaf-15bcd1ca6b37) is our main priority, don't worry about buying  [Multi-Tool](item_5ba8d94e-f2f3-44b7-8773-025fc6ed7c56) if you can't afford it.

---

# 💰 High Cash

-  [Custom Stock](item_17d633af-8bcc-4893-b865-be0a7bc66fe2) is a great item for this build, you can make great use from both the AP and the Weapon Power.
- Buy AP/Weapon Power from Green Items.

---

# 📝 TL;DR

- 

---

# 🎮 Playstyle

- When the round starts and people throw out their cooldowns/spam to get some early Ultimate Charge, try to deflect what you can for extra early Ultimate Charge. Make sure to stay alive until Javelin Spin is back off cooldown for another attempt and with some Energy Javelins weaved inbetween, you should have a very fast Terra-Surge to win the first fight with. Try to snowball this advantage to win the round.
- With Ability Power, your Terra-Surge will charge up even higher and make it more lethal.

---

# ⚡ Power

-  [Centripetal Charge](item_4c59fa91-c687-4c6d-810d-ddb79288315a): Makes our Ultimate require 25% less meaning we can get it even quicker. It also makes cooldowns reset on use, so feel free to use both Fortify and Javelin Spin to charge in the enemy team to get the best Terra-Surge you can.

---

# 🧰 Items

-  [Junker Whatchamajig](item_b81ebab8-5c85-405a-b28d-2496de33cd9c): The extra 25% Starting Ultimate Charge can provide us with some great cheese for this round and is pretty fun to use. Combined with  [Centripetal Charge](item_4c59fa91-c687-4c6d-810d-ddb79288315a), that's 50% of our regular Ultimate Charge already.
-  [Energized Bracers](item_f83a1d9e-91f8-4d2c-bd62-c673b8d9fd2e) is just extra Ability Power to spend our Cash on and we can also get some good value from the Ability Lifesteal. Feel free to replace this with  [Biolight Overflow](item_1220eaec-f913-4de2-816c-0dc070b285d0) if you want to.

---

# 💸 Low Cash

- Forego  [Energized Bracers](item_f83a1d9e-91f8-4d2c-bd62-c673b8d9fd2e) for any other AP you can afford.

---

# 💰 High Cash

- Purchase  [Nano Cola](item_79b22609-8046-4a8a-a5a2-bb49cd7e11c6) instead.
- Or instead of trying to cheese with  [Junker Whatchamajig](item_b81ebab8-5c85-405a-b28d-2496de33cd9c), just purchase  [Catalytic Crystal](item_3e3f4f77-cdf8-4dda-a5b0-2fb9390aefc4) instead.

---

# 📝 TL;DR

- We now gain more Ultimate Charge from our Javelin Spin and Energy Javelin and our Terra-Surge will now slow enemies we catch with it even more.

---

# 🎮 Playstyle

- Keep using Javelin Spin to deflect projectiles to farm Terra-Surge quicker.
- Terra-Surge will now slow enemies inside it more and charging it close to ~300% should be enough to kill squishies. One it charges over 300%, it starts to ramp up really fast, so bare that in mind if you're trying to kill a Tank. Always pop it before the last enemy escapes if you are holding on to it, unless you're zoning to prevent a recontest on the objective.
- Charge in to the enemy carry with Fortify and Javelin Spin to force them to use their escape cooldown and then use Terra-Surge to pull them back in.

---

# 🧰 Items

-  [Catalytic Crystal](item_3e3f4f77-cdf8-4dda-a5b0-2fb9390aefc4) will make our AP-empowered abilities generate us more Ultimate Charge.
-  [Liquid Nitrogen](item_a8d99526-05a3-4405-babb-b025479b1b98) will make our Ultimate slow down enemies caught in it even further. I believe this item stacks and makes it a 50% slow.

---

# 💸 Low Cash

- Sell Green items to afford the purples if needed. If you have to skip one, skip [Liquid Nitrogen](item_a8d99526-05a3-4405-babb-b025479b1b98).

---

# 💰 High Cash

- Buy as much AP as you can with extra Cash.

---

# 📝 TL;DR

- Continue playing the same way. Now your Terra-Surge will provide extra utility to your team to follow up.

---

# 🎮 Playstyle

- Continue using Javelin Spin and Energy Javelin to farm your Ultimate as fast as possible.
- Continue using Terra-Surge to secure kills.

---

# ⚡ Power

-  [Supercharger](item_3b888b9f-1c3a-47ce-8326-41f2a312d66f): This will enable your team to better follow up on enemies caught in your Ultimate. It's a 50% slow now thanks to  [Liquid Nitrogen](item_a8d99526-05a3-4405-babb-b025479b1b98).

---

# 🧰 Items

- We just want to buy more Ability Power and Cooldown Reduction from now.
- This round we upgrade our greens.
-  [Nano Cola](item_79b22609-8046-4a8a-a5a2-bb49cd7e11c6) and  [Multi-Tool](item_5ba8d94e-f2f3-44b7-8773-025fc6ed7c56) give us more AP and Cooldown Reduction.

---

# 💸 Low Cash

- Just keep some greens with what you can afford. Buy whatever AP you can.

---

# 💰 High Cash

- Buy  [Champion's Kit](item_8682f8c7-8811-439b-8d50-fa81cd43ddce) if you can afford it.

---

# 📝 TL;DR

- Keep playing the same way, we just do more damage now.
---

# 🎮 Playstyle

- Continue using Javelin Spin and Energy Javelin to farm your Ultimate as fast as possible.
- Continue using Terra-Surge to secure kills.

---

# 🧰 Items

- Replace  [Multi-Tool](item_5ba8d94e-f2f3-44b7-8773-025fc6ed7c56) with  [Champion's Kit](item_8682f8c7-8811-439b-8d50-fa81cd43ddce) for more damage!

- Buy a cheaper upgrade like  [Iridescent Iris](item_b7fb28ef-ce82-416b-8693-01c274f8df4e) or  [Lumerico Fusion Drive](item_3da81000-333c-460a-a1a2-09441bfda9c8) or  [Custom Stock](item_17d633af-8bcc-4893-b865-be0a7bc66fe2) if you're really broke.

# 💰 High Cash

-  Buy extra item from: [Iridescent Iris](item_b7fb28ef-ce82-416b-8693-01c274f8df4e)   [Lumerico Fusion Drive](item_3da81000-333c-460a-a1a2-09441bfda9c8)   [Energized Bracers](item_f83a1d9e-91f8-4d2c-bd62-c673b8d9fd2e)   [Custom Stock](item_17d633af-8bcc-4893-b865-be0a7bc66fe2) 

---

# 📝 TL;DR

- Javelin Spin and Energy Javelin have lowered cooldowns, use them more.

---

# 🎮 Playstyle

- Continue using Javelin Spin and Energy Javelin to farm your Ultimate as fast as possible.
- Continue using Terra-Surge to secure kills.
- With a total of 35% Cooldown Reduction during Fortify for our 2 core abilities, Javelin Spin is now on 5.2s cooldown and Energy Javelin is on 3.9s cooldown when used during Fortify. **Remember that you're going to be super vulnerable when Fortify and Javelin Spin are both on cooldown**.

---

# ⚡ Power

-  [Factory Reset](item_d98df807-9dd6-4553-96bb-a1b49a0fe169): Lower cooldowns on Javelin Spin and Energy Javelin, so spam them more to farm Terra-Surge quicker.
- **TIP**: You can use Fortify after Javelin Spin ends and it will still reduce the remaining cooldown by 35%. This can stop you from overlapping Fortify with Javelin Spin too much.

---

# 🧰 Items

- Buy  [Iridescent Iris](item_b7fb28ef-ce82-416b-8693-01c274f8df4e) for more Ability Power and Cooldown Reduction.

---

# 💸 Low Cash

- Buy  [Multi-Tool](item_5ba8d94e-f2f3-44b7-8773-025fc6ed7c56) instead

---

# 💰 High Cash

- Replace  [Nano Cola](item_79b22609-8046-4a8a-a5a2-bb49cd7e11c6) with  [Efi’s Theorem](item_609c4cb6-a232-4e08-a11f-5252d40382be)
